# Web3Forms — https://web3forms.com
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=

# Production site (optional fallback; browser uses window.location.origin)
VITE_SITE_URL=https://alimanrouh.com

# --- Deploy checklist for https://alimanrouh.com (Hostinger / public_html) ---
# 1. Copy .env.example → .env locally; set VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY, then rebuild (.env is not committed).
# 2. npm run build
# 3. On the server, DELETE old site files in public_html (keep backups if needed):
#    - index.html, assets/, images/, favicon.png, .htaccess, etc.
# 4. Upload the ENTIRE dist/ folder contents to public_html in one deploy:
#    - index.html + assets/* must come from the same build (hashes must match).
# 5. Confirm dist/.htaccess was uploaded (SPA fallback for /contact, /about, etc.).
# 6. Purge Hostinger cache / CDN cache; hard-refresh the browser (Ctrl+Shift+R).
# 7. Verify: open / and /contact — no 404 on /assets/index-*.js or CSS.
# 8. Web3Forms dashboard → Form settings → Restrict to Domain (if enabled):
#    - alimanrouh.com
#    - www.alimanrouh.com (if you use www)
# 9. Autoresponder logo (Pro): https://alimanrouh.com/images/brand/logo-primary.png
